First Department,

June, 1983

(June 2, 1983) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Burton Kagan, Appellant.

— Judgment, Supreme Court, New York County (Herbert Altman, J.), rendered on January 5, 1982, unanimously affirmed. The case is remitted to the Supreme Court, New York County, for further proceedings pursuant to CPL 460.50 (subd 5). No opinion. Concur — Murphy, P. J., Bloom, Fein, Milonas and Kassal, JJ.
